    <div class="section">
        <h2>Executive Summary</h2>
        <p>Game Show Studios in Sacramento and San Diego lit up from June to August 2025 with 200 survey responses, scoring an NPS of 69. Guests loved the fun, high-energy atmosphere, charismatic hosts, and the perfect vibe for team building and birthdays, with 80% saying it was even more fun than escape rooms. Key opportunities emerged around session length, tech reliability, game design tweaks, perceived value, and rare fairness concerns. Top fixes: longer sessions, smoother tech, refined games, and fairness safeguards.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>NPS Breakdown: Spin the Wheel of Scores!</h2>
        <p>Net Promoter Score (NPS = % Promoters [9-10] - % Detractors [0-6]) measures guest loyalty:</p>
        <table>
            <tr>
                <th>Metric</th>
